General.Name: HUBLine Bhd
General.Description: Hubline Berhad, an investment holding company, provides dry bulk shipping services in the Southeast Asian Region. The company offers cargo services for coal, gypsum, palm kernel shells, feldspar, scrap metals, and sand. It also owns and charters ships; and provides management services. In addition, the company sells machine parts and accessories; provides repair and maintenance services for equipment; offers aircraft chartering and maintenance services; and operates a shipping agency, as well as provides helicopter and fixed wing flight training services. It operates through a fleet of tugs and barges at various ports in Cambodia, Indonesia, Malaysia, the Philippines, Thailand, and Vietnam. Hubline Berhad is based in Miri, Malaysia.
